      #}
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h2>Contribute to LibreCores</h2>
      <p>LibreCores is a true community project. All development is done in the open, and we're always open to new contributors!
      If you have only a couple of minutes to spare, or a full week, there's something for you to do.</p>
      <p>Have a look at our contribution guide and get started today!</p>
      <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://librecores-web.readthedocs.io/en/latest/contributing.html">Read on how to contribute to LibreCores &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
